OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FA community has rallied around a Grade
OL,8,FII listed church and its parishioners
OL,9,Fafter the building and gravestones
OL,10,Fwere vandalised in a suspected hate
OL,11,Fcrime on Good Friday.
OL,13,FLewd images and offensive phrases were
OL,14,Fdaubed on the walls of St James Church
OL,15,Fin Leyland, near Preston, as well as
OL,16,Fon dozens of gravestones, forcing the
OL,17,Fchurch to hide the graffiti with
OL,18,Fplants before a wedding on Saturday.
