OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FLancashire Police said the
OL,8,F"disgraceful act of vandalism" was
OL,9,F"being treated as a hate crime", and
OL,10,Fno arrests have been made, while
OL,11,Finquiries continue.
OL,13,FBut, despite the vandalism, Vicar Marc
OL,14,FWolverson says those in the local
OL,15,Fcommunity have come together to help
OL,16,Fremove some of the offensive messages,
OL,17,Fallowing the church to celebrate the
OL,18,FEaster weekend.
