OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,F"My first reaction was heartbreak at
OL,8,Fthe actions of these individuals who
OL,9,Fperpetrated this crime; I feel very
OL,10,Fsorry for them," he said.
OL,12,F"It's the worst thing I've had to deal
OL,13,Fwith as a vicar.
OL,15,F"But, in the days since, the way we
OL,16,Fhave seen the people of Leyland rally
OL,17,Fround to help has been so uplifting.
