OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,F"The wedding we had planned on
OL,8,FSaturday was able to go ahead and we
OL,9,Fhave continued with all our services
OL,10,Facross the Easter weekend... one of
OL,11,Fthe holiest periods in the Christian
OL,12,Fcalendar."
OL,14,FAfter the news of the crime, the
OL,15,FArchbishop of York, currently the most
OL,16,Fsenior Church of England leader, sent
OL,17,Fa message of support to Mr Wolverson
OL,18,Fand the people of the Church of
OL,19,FEngland parish.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]
