OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FIn his letter, the archbishop said:
OL,8,F"For this precious holy ground to be
OL,9,Fso appallingly desecrated is deeply
OL,10,Fshocking.
OL,12,F"Easter should be a time of
OL,13,Fcelebration and joy.
OL,15,F"It saddens me greatly that this
OL,16,FEaster your own celebrations may feel
OL,17,Fa little muted."
OL,19,FHe added: "Yet, of course, the story
OL,20,Fof Easter is the story of God's
OL,21,Ftriumph over sin and darkness.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@PO]{D@KOU
