OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,F"Because God raised Jesus from the
OL,8,Fdead, we know that no power on earth
OL,9,Fcan undermine his mercy and love.
OL,11,F"I hope it is a small comfort to know
OL,12,Fthat, alongside many others, I am
OL,13,Fholding you and your church in my
OL,14,Fprayers this Easter.
OL,16,F"I am praying that despite the horrors
OL,17,Fof Good Friday, your faith in the
OL,18,Fresurrection might be strengthened and
OL,19,Fthat you will all experience anew the
OL,20,Fpower of the Lord at work in your
OL,21,Flives."
