OL,3,C'It's the worst thing I've dealt
OL,4,Cwith': Community rally as church
OL,5,Cvandalised
OL,7,FRt Rev Philip North, Bishop of
OL,8,FBlackburn, also voiced support for the
OL,9,Fparish, saying: "It is good news that
OL,10,Fthe police are taking this disgraceful
OL,11,Fand shocking incident with a great
OL,12,Fdeal of seriousness and are treating
OL,13,Fit as a hate crime."
OL,15,FLocal councillor Paul Wharton-Hardman
OL,16,Fsaid members of the local community
OL,17,Fgathered to start cleaning the
OL,18,Fgraffiti off the walls and over 40
OL,19,Fgravestones from 6am on Saturday
OL,20,Fmorning.
