OL,7,FIn a Facebook post, the Labour deputy
OL,8,Fmayor for South Ribble Borough Council
OL,9,Fadded: "The community got together
OL,10,Fthrough fumes and tears, they helped
OL,11,Frestore dignity to every stone they
OL,12,Ftouched.
OL,14,F"The work isn't finished yet, but it's
OL,15,Fwell on the way."
